---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import logo from "../assets/logo1.jpg";
import heroImage from "../assets/header.jpg";
const { title = "BPR Mangun Pundiyasa" } = Astro.props;
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{title}</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #0f4c81;
      --secondary: #f5f7fa;
      --accent: #d9e8f5;
      --text: #1f2937;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: white;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
	  position: sticky;
	  top: 0;
	  z-index: 1000;

	  background: var(--primary);
	  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
	  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);

	  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);

	  color: white;
	  padding: 1rem 2rem;

	  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
	}

    nav {
	  display: flex;
	  justify-content: space-between;
	  align-items: center;

	  max-width: 1200px;
	  margin: 0 auto;
	}

    .logo-link {
	  text-decoration: none;
	  color: inherit;
	  transition: transform 0.25s ease;
	}

	.logo-link:hover {
	  transform: scale(1.05);
	}

    .logo img {
      width: 50px;
      height: 50px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
	
	.logo-link {
	  text-decoration: none;
	  color: inherit;
	}

	.logo {
	  display: flex;
	  align-items: center;
	  gap: 0.75rem;
	}

	.logo-link:hover {
	  opacity: 0.9;
	}

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .nav-links {
	  display: flex;
	  gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.nav-links a {
	  position: relative;
	  overflow: hidden;

	  color: white;
	  text-decoration: none;
	  font-weight: 600;

	  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
	  border-radius: 999px;

	  transition:
		transform 0.25s ease,
		background-color 0.25s ease,
		box-shadow 0.25s ease;
	}

	/* Shine effect */
	.nav-links a::before {
	  content: "";
	  position: absolute;

	  top: -20%;
	  left: -200%;

	  width: 80px;
	  height: 140%;

	  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);

	  filter: blur(10px);
	  transform: rotate(20deg);

	  transition: left 0.7s ease;
	}

	.nav-links a:hover {
	  transform: translateY(-3px);

	  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);

	  box-shadow:
		0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15),
		0 0 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
	}

	.nav-links a::before {
	  content: "";

	  position: absolute;
	  top: 0;
	  left: -50%;

	  width: 50%;
	  height: 100%;

	  background: linear-gradient(
		120deg,
		transparent,
		rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5),
		transparent
	  );

	  transform: skewX(-25deg) translateX(-300%);
	  pointer-events: none;
	}

	.nav-links a:hover::before {
	  animation: navShine 0.7s ease forwards;
	}

	@keyframes navShine {
	  0% {
		transform: skewX(-25deg) translateX(-300%);
		opacity: 0;
	  }

	  15% {
		opacity: 1;
	  }

	  100% {
		transform: skewX(-25deg) translateX(600%);
		opacity: 0;
	  }
	}

	/* Underline animation */
	.nav-links a::after {
	  content: "";

	  position: absolute;
	  left: 20%;
	  bottom: 6px;

	  width: 60%;
	  height: 2px;

	  background: white;

	  transform: scaleX(0);
	  transform-origin: center;

	  transition: transform 0.25s ease;
	}

	.nav-links a:hover::after {
	  transform: scaleX(1);
	}

    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
    }

    footer {
	  background: var(--primary);
	  color: white;
	  text-align: center;
	  padding: 1rem;
	  margin-top: 4rem;
	}

	footer a,
	footer a:visited {
	  color: white;
	  text-decoration: none;
	}

	footer a:hover {
	  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
	  text-decoration: underline;
	}

	footer a:active {
	  color: white;
	}
	

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <nav>
		<a href="/" class="logo-link">
		  <div class="logo">
			<Image
			  src={logo}
			  alt="Logo BPR Mangun Pundiyasa"
			  width={50}
			  height={50}
			/>
			<h2>BPR Mangun Pundiyasa</h2>
		  </div>
		 </a>

      <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="/">Beranda</a>
          <a href="/services">Layanan</a>
          <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
          <a href="/contact">Hubungi Kami</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <slot />
  </main>

  <footer>
	<p>Bank merupakan peserta penjaminan LPS.</p>
<p>Maksimum nilai simpanan yang dijamin LPS per nasabah per bank adalah Rp 2 Miliar.<p>

<p>PT. BPR Mangun Pundiyasa Berizin dan diawasi (OJK) Otoritas Jasa Keuangan.</p>

<p>Informasi tingkat Bunga Penjaminan: <a href="https://apps.lps.go.id/BankPesertaLPSRate" https://apps.lps.go.id/BankPesertaLPSRate>https://apps.lps.go.id/BankPesertaLPSRate</a></p>
    <h3><br>© 2026 PT. BPR Mangun Pundiyasa</h3>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>